“Never ask me about Jon,”, he said, cold as ice.“He
is my blood, and that is all you need to know.And now I will learn
where you heard that name, my lady.”, She had pledged to obey;

“Robert, I ask you, what did we rise against Aerys Targaryen
for, if not to put an end to the murder of children?”,
“To put an end to Targaryens!”, the king growled.
